text: Patrik Eli치코 (born April 13, 1976) is a former Czech professional ice hockey winger that played for the New Jersey Devils of the National Hockey League (NHL) where he was the alternate captain. == Other websites == *Official website * * Category:1976 births Category:Living people Category:Albany River Rats players Category:Czech ice hockey players Category:New Jersey Devils players Category:Olympic bronze medalists for the Czech Republic Category:Stanley Cup champions
